{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.1", "text_original": "采薇采薇，薇亦作止。曰歸曰歸，歲亦莫止。\n靡室靡家，玁狁之故。不遑啟居，玁狁之故。", "text_normalized": "采薇采薇，薇亦作止。曰歸曰歸，歲亦莫止。\n靡室靡家，玁狁之故。不遑啟居，玁狁之故。", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.2", "text_original": "采薇采薇，薇亦柔止。曰歸曰歸，心亦憂止。\n憂心烈烈，載飢載渴。我戍未定，靡使歸聘。", "text_normalized": "采薇采薇，薇亦柔止。曰歸曰歸，心亦憂止。\n憂心烈烈，載飢載渴。我戍未定，靡使歸聘。", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.3", "text_original": "采薇采薇，薇亦剛止。曰歸曰歸，歲亦陽止。\n王事靡盬，不遑啟處。憂心孔疚，我行不來。", "text_normalized": "采薇采薇，薇亦剛止。曰歸曰歸，歲亦陽止。\n王事靡盬，不遑啟處。憂心孔疚，我行不來。", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.4", "text_original": "彼爾維何？維常之華。彼路斯何？君子之車。\n戎車既駕，四牡業業。豈敢定居？一月三捷。", "text_normalized": "彼爾維何？維常之華。彼路斯何？君子之車。\n戎車既駕，四牡業業。豈敢定居？一月三捷。", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.5", "text_original": "駕彼四牡，四牡騤騤。君子所依，小人所腓。\n四牡翼翼，象弭魚服。豈不日戒，玁狁孔棘！", "text_normalized": "駕彼四牡，四牡騤騤。君子所依，小人所腓。\n四牡翼翼，象弭魚服。豈不日戒，玁狁孔棘！", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-007__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.6", "text_original": "昔我往矣，楊柳依依。今我來思，雨雪霏霏。\n行道遲遲，載渴載飢。我心傷悲，莫知我哀！", "text_normalized": "昔我往矣，楊柳依依。今我來思，雨雪霏霏。\n行道遲遲，載渴載飢。我心傷悲，莫知我哀！", "notes": "采薇 Chinese stanza 6."}
